5.title: Episode #6.5
5.plot: Two former Nexus members clash in the main event, as Heath Slater takes to the ring to go one one one with former ally, Justin Gabriel. The recent problems between Leo Kruger and Richie Steamboat lead to in-ring confrontation. Plus, Raquel Diaz makes her debut, Jinder Mahal takes on 'Showtime' Percy Watson, and more.
